&lt;li&gt;Analyze and regularly review student assessment data – both formally and informally - to drive curricular and pedagogical choices and adjustments;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maximize learning time through effective classroom management;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide an inviting, exciting, learning environment using varied instructional techniques that accommodate all learning styles and developmentally appropriate strategies;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for and mastery/deep knowledge in instructional subject area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evidence of student achievement growth in previous teaching roles;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong desire to collaborate with other faculty and instructional leaders to discuss student work and ensure curricular coherence;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong desire to engage families through intentional relationship building and ongoing communication;&lt;/li&gt;
